<tr><td bgcolor="#3F403F" width="98%" class="cheader">Type I: Advanced Decks</td><td bgcolor="3F403F" valign="top" align="right" width="22"><img src="/starwarsccg/gfx/theme1/topcorner.gif" width="23" height="22" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="0" align="right"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="98%" colspan=2><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" class="cbody">
<tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">TRM EBOX - It chokes, it kills, it&#39;s fun!</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><table width='84' border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'><tr><td background='/swtcg/gfx/5star.gif'><img src='/lotr/gfx/trans.gif' width='1' height='19'></td></tr></table><font size=1>(4.18)</font> | <A HREF="/starwarsccg/decks/decks.php?reviews=31647&PHPSESSID=7256ac780cef1a43d27bb5fd5f225bdb">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/starwarsccg/main/mpage.php?member=15980">Tim "Aglets" Simon</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/starwarsccg/main/mpage.php?member=15980&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> This deck combines force denial with intense damage to relentlessly pound your opponent.  Who doesn&#39;t want to play with a bunch of X-wings?</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> February 27, 2004</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Starting:  (6)<br />
<br />
